                    { "tt0400243", "Willy Smax", "In the last programme Bob Monkhouse ever worked on before he died he picked all his favourite comedy clips from his lifetime. Too ill to contribute the programme instead featured narration and contributions from fellow professionals.", "N/A", "21 Jan 2004", "Bob Monkhouse's Comedy Heroes" },
