                    { "tt0863059", "Sarah Ball, Jocelyn Stevenson", "In this all new feature length special , Bob the Builder and his team of machines travel to the Winter Games in snowy Bobblesberg. Their job is to build a log cabin for the Bobsville Mayoress but a huge snow storm hits and leaves the event building machines stranded en route. Team Leader Scoop is joined by brand new characters Benny and Zoomer for their biggest ever challenge. There're lots to do and the clock is ticking: can they build it?", "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTU2MjA5NzA4OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzE0MTA2MDE@._V1_SX300.jpg", "28 Sep 2004", "Bob the Builder: Snowed Under" },
                    { "tt0876255", "Stu Schreiberg", "N/A", "N/A", "16 Sep 2006", "Bob & Tom: Standup Sitting Down" },
                    { "tt0880606", "Steve Bentley", "Bob is quite familiar with the art of using a go between and prefabricated breakup lines to end a relationship. Having been dumped himself by his girlfriend s drunk friend, Jill, Bob decides to make a career out of delivering breakup o grams to others. Jared, bewildered on how to breakup with his crazy girlfriend, turns to Bob for help, but this breakup has something else in store for Bob; Her name is Natalie.", "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjA3ODAwMzQzOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTUzNzkzMQ@@._V1_SX300.jpg", "09 Aug 2006", "Break-up Bob" },
                    { "tt0890906", "N/A", "N/A", "N/A", "13 Jan 1993", "Bob Mann's Automatic Golf" },
                    { "tt0893311", "Stu Maddux", "A self-told story about two men who met in the service, confronted the troops in their unit 52 years ago and went on to live the rest of their lives together.", "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTQwMTM2Mzg1MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNDk5NjM1MQ@@._V1_SX300.jpg", "06 Jun 2006", "Bob and Jack's 52-Year Adventure" },
                    { "tt0924168", "N/A", "A cartoon series starring two rabbits who live in a magician's top hat. Bob and Bobby are two fun little characters who think up something new to do every day. Even with the best of intentions sometimes things go wrong, but their jolly adventures usually have a practical message: exercising is healthy, work can be fun, and sharing is a great way to be a good friend. Bob and Bobby also tell kids to never cheat, be lazy or start fights - and also that it's wise to eat plenty of carrots.", "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZmIwYmNkNGYtN2Y4Yy00ZGNiLTliZDAtMDAzNjE4Y2UzYTRiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjIxMzMyMQ@@._V1_SX300.jpg", "11 Dec 1979", "Bob and Bobby - Top Hat Rabbits" },
                    { "tt0945703", "N/A", "La toute première télé-réalité plus vraie que nature au Québec, où les petits détails de la vie quotidienne deviennent des événements lorsqu'ils son vécus par notre méga Bob Gratton. Nous serons les témoins privilégiés de ses premières expériences dans une soirée pour célibataires, ses premières expériences dans un centre de thalassothérapie et de sa participation au Défilé de la Fierté Gaie en tant que «guérisseur d'homosexuels».", "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjI2ODA1MjMzMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNTc1NTQ5Mw@@._V1_SX300.jpg", "15 Jan 2007", "Bob Gratton, ma vie/My Life" },
                    { "tt0948667", "Burton L. King", "Bob Mason, after a big cattle shipment, leaves the ranch house for the city, and there he woos and wins Kittie Gray. After the wedding they return to the ranch, where Kittie, as the months go by, becomes tired of the new life and accepts the attentions of Jack Duncan. She agrees to elope with him. However, they are overtaken by the infuriated husband, who, while he spares Duncan's life, thrashes him within an inch of his life. Kittie returns with her husband. She really loves him, but as the months pass she comes to believe that she has forfeited her husband's love. Duncan has not forgotten Kittie. He plots with Pedro, an outlaw, and they visit the ranch house one night, planning to take the girl away by force. Kittie confronts them with a revolver, and as she holds them helpless before the weapon, her husband and friends arrive, and the villains meet their just deserts. Then it is that Bob Mason appreciates the faithfulness and love of his wife.", "N/A", "13 Jan 1917", "The Making of Bob Mason's Wife" },
