                    { "tt1119179", "Michael Simon", "Broadcast daily on over 150 radio stations, The Bob & Tom Show is one of the most successful comedy radio shows in the country. Now in this all-star event, the comedians who have helped make Bob & Tom a morning ritual for over 5 million listeners come together on-stage for one sold-out night. This event, taped live at the historic Paramount Theatre in Anderson, Indiana, features the very best of the friends of Bob & Tom including: David Crowe, Mike Birbiglia, Nick Griffin, Ralph Harris and Greg Warren.", "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMjA4Mjg3MTc4OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTcxMjA2MDE@._V1_SX300.jpg", "11 Sep 2007", "Bob & Tom Comedy All-Stars Tour" },
