                    { "tt1150932", "N/A", "This Fall, it's an all new season on ABC...inspired by the biggest stars...and the best new shows... Take a sneak-peek at the all new ABC Fall lineup, and most importantly, answer the question \"Who is Bob Patterson and why is everyone talking about him?\" The Number Three Self-Help Guru in the Nation is taking an all new season to the top. The best new shows...the hottest stars...and Bob Patterson...Definitely ABC.", "N/A", "03 Sep 2001", "The ABC Fall Preview Special: An All New Season Inspired by Bob Patterson" },
                    { "tt1150935", "Sid Smith", "On this festive and tropical Holiday outing, Bob Hope introduces The Associated Press- All American Football Team. Mother and daughter country duo, The Judds, sing Winter Wonderland and Beautiful Star of Bethlehem and Bob and Barbara Eden perform his signature Christmas song, Silver Bells. Comedy bits include a spoof of the hit movie Steel Magnolias. Entitled Steel Petunias, the skit has Bob Hope dressed in drag as the Dolly Parton character, Miss Trudy !", "N/A", "16 Dec 1989", "Bob Hope's Christmas Special from Waikoloa, Hawaii" },
