                    { "tt1297801", "Sonia Anderson", "He was and is, without doubt, Jamaica's finest export and in this programme we can reveal for the first time the behind the scenes Bob Marley that only his closest confidantes could know.", "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTA5OTk4MTA1MzZeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDA1ODIwNjAx._V1_SX300.jpg", "01 Aug 2007", "Bob Marley: Freedom Road" },
