                    { "tt13148254", "David Scarbrough", "When history was made, Bob Gomel was there. This documentary examines the stories behind the stories of some of the most significant events in the 20th century. Hear and see the history unfold from the perspective of a legendary LIFE Magazine photographer.", "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZmM3NzZlYWQtMTIyYS00MTg1LWI0OGItYWFlMThkNGRiMWJkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTEyNDU4NjEw._V1_SX300.jpg", "21 Sep 2020", "Bob Gomel: Eyewitness" },
