                    { "tt2165867", "Joel Gilbert", "At first called \"Dylan's God-Awful Gospel\" by his most loyal fans, Bob Dylan's Jesus Years is today regarded as among the best of his career. How did a Jewish folk singer from the mid-west come to Jesus?", "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTQ5Nzg4MzI5MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjI1NjA2MDE@._V1_SX300.jpg", "28 Oct 2008", "Inside Bob Dylan's Jesus Years: Busy Being Born... Again!" },
                    { "tt2166179", "Patrick Shawn Bennett", "Chapter 1 in a retro style throwback to the cliffhanger serials of the '30s & '40s. Bob Strong, an American adventurer in 1940s Africa, gets caught up in a Nazi plot to build a super weapon. He and his friends take on the mission to stop the Nazis but they get side tracked when they encounter a killer gorilla known as \"Bokato. \"", "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTAzMDQzNDk2MjdeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU3MDQ3MDYzMjc@._V1_SX300.jpg", "01 Dec 2011", "The Adventures of Gorilla Bob: Bokato Attacks!" },
