                    { "tt2290635", "N/A", "Dr. Bob Ballard, the man who discovered the Titanic's final resting place in 1985, travels to Ireland to meet some of the men who helped build the ship and discusses how the ship's remains are in danger from looters, among other t...", "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTY5ODY5NjQxNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzQwNzA2MDE@._V1_SX300.jpg", "09 Apr 2012", "Save the Titanic with Bob Ballard" },
