                    { "tt3171082", "Rydrea Walker", "A boy named Bob Phillips, who always happy all times and funny, but he is fall in love with new girl named Jaylea Wilson, he really want her so bad and he feel for her. He never tell Jaylea how his feel for her, In high School, Bob finally admitted tell Jaylea that he feel for her.", "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMGZlY2Y4NmYtYzBkMy00NTFlLWEzMDAtNjQ4OTFjYzM3Y2JkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTQxODAxNzM@._V1_SX300.jpg", "15 Feb 2013", "Bob Movie" },
                    { "tt3183924", "John Rafferty", "After tragedy strikes, Bob Karate is a broken man, a man who has given up, a man who cannot find meaning in life. His two sons struggle to keep the family ship from sinking, while sorting out the complexities of their own lives. At times funny, at times sad, and at times surreal, 'Bob Karate' is a one-of-a-kind short film, chock-full of of colorful characters, whose journeys weave in and out in this unique short film.", "N/A", "N/A", "Bob Karate" },
                    { "tt3202340", "N/A", "Having fun is getting it done, especially when Bob the Builder and his best friends are here to help! Watch and learn as Bob rescues his pal Scruffy, repairs an old theater, builds a stage, and throws a surprise birthday party for his best friend Wendy. Get the help you need from Bob the Builder in these heartwarming tales of teamwork and adventure.", "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTY5OTQwODM5OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTkzODA2MDE@._V1_SX300.jpg", "01 Feb 2012", "Bob the Builder: Here to Help" },
                    { "tt3216286", "Kimberly Duran, Alexis Garcia, Joseph Williams", "Bob Bates: A Legacy of Creativity is a short student documentary that traces the life of the founder of Inner-City Arts, an arts education center in downtown Los Angeles. Written, directed, edited and filmed by high school students currently attending classes at Inner-City Arts, the documentary is more than a linear tale. The students show how Bob follows his creativity 'wherever it takes him' to end up in Skid Row starting an art school 25 years ago. The results take the audience on a journey from his life as a professional artist living on a chicken ranch to his current project creating an innovative 'Creativity Lab' at Inner-City Arts.", "N/A", "N/A", "Bob Bates: A Legacy of Creativity" },
