                    { "tt3328944", "Babak Shokrian", "At 40, the road less traveled is narrowing for Bob who struggles to write his next screenplay while dealing with eccentric tenants, unclogging drains and collecting rents, for his father's real estate business. But when his father falls ill, Bob decides to change and embrace the legacy of his family and culture for the first time. He even finds himself falling in love with a Jewish Iranian 'princess' from the community. But can he really change?", "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzc1MzMwMTY4OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDY1NzY1NTE@._V1_SX300.jpg", "25 Sep 2015", "Shah Bob" },
